{"tid":2274414,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"理大圍城一周年成驚弓之鳥急「封校」 即日起至月底拒傳媒訪客入校園","createTime":"2020-11-06T12:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T15:44:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d76ea687ba0e3b02e90692381ceeba2759fdae","tid":2274414,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZkCXNipltOpuUuhKTuiTqfc-uFE=/802x402/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7TPOVJ6BHJBFHOYB5QLIWHZMDE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZkCXNipltOpuUuhKTuiTqfc-uFE%3D%2F802x402%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7TPOVJ6BHJBFHOYB5QLIWHZMDE.jpg&h=f2bb2202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年11月爆發「理大圍城」，事件踏入1周年之際，理工大學成驚弓之鳥，「封校」拒絕傳媒和訪客到訪。理大今日向師生發通告指，即日起至本月底收緊校園出入口管制，只有教職員、學生和獲預先授權者可進入校園，訪客要獲學系主任或學生事務處「特別批准」才可進入，此前已透過訪客登記系統登記的，亦需要重新申請。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，理大高層近日開會商討，認為本月是敏感日子，不想「理大圍城」事件再發酵，決定採取「封校」措施。《蘋果》已向理大查詢，正等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/TROGATTKYBC6NEXCHNIJ5KIOHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FTROGATTKYBC6NEXCHNIJ5KIOHA%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9vGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=2b1d07d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FTROGATTKYBC6NEXCHNIJ5KIOHA%2F&h=63ff94e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/TROGATTKYBC6NEXCHNIJ5KIOHA/</a>"},{"pid":"f82cbafe4f4a4142176aae3a21bb7f415212cb42","tid":2274414,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VJOhTwv7kPjSsrzs0nxQTvAwklQ=/1536x376/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y4TI5O3KVJAD5BADZ5WUO6MR4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVJOhTwv7kPjSsrzs0nxQTvAwklQ%3D%2F1536x376%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY4TI5O3KVJAD5BADZ5WUO6MR4E.jpg&h=967d0280&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2954c2f9964e242f044f2ffe0ba7a8fa45aa8016","tid":2274414,"uid":273703,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d72e9c006d6044adbedd7caf4e072c3055eb11bc","tid":2274414,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:03:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78459f102e078a7993d0c8a67186ea24ce4da3e8","tid":2274414,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2954c2f9964e242f044f2ffe0ba7a8fa45aa8016","tid":2274414,"uid":273703,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc39e5d67e5ceb9e3a5328ff9436282c56fe6bc1","tid":2274414,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n又黎<br />\n<br />\n中大已經係咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea43efadecbc2e5780600b26b1678a5bf13fe8d6","tid":2274414,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:03:35.000Z","msg":"據理大教職員提供的訪客登記系統使用手冊，訪客原本可因「各種業務原因」（various business reasons）到訪理大，教職員可為其邀請的訪客作登記，登記要在訪客到訪前最少24小時前完成，有關訪客會獲發QR code，並可憑該QR code進入校園。<br />\n<br />\n理大學生會前外務副會長鄭其浩指，聽聞有關改動與學校安全顧問因應「理大圍城1周年」，建議校方提升戒備級別有關。他形容改動十分突然且擾民，將影響不少師生親友到訪理大的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n鄭又稱，校方先入為主地認為學生以及學生會必定會於此段期間「搞事」，對此表示遺憾。他續指，明日將就此與校方會面，了解校方突然收緊校園出入政策的原因及相關措施。"},{"pid":"ca4a4d5f98bc6f456bc89cc0bc97fc77b377e246","tid":2274414,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:04:26.000Z","msg":"校獨"},{"pid":"7b6062a74317b70ecfd59a63506d30f8e8a919ec","tid":2274414,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:05:40.000Z","msg":"ON9"},{"pid":"3b1ae5db0030837aed4c91e45716a35f05246222","tid":2274414,"uid":305767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只有中、小學、幼稚園先唔對外開放，香港已無大學"},{"pid":"5b22166f51707f0f611ab05369d6065bfa17f644","tid":2274414,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc39e5d67e5ceb9e3a5328ff9436282c56fe6bc1","tid":2274414,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n又黎<br />\n<br />\n中大已經係咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"中大而家唔係曬證登記入得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ecd49a0bd42191f26147ceda8f935fd7382ce0","tid":2274414,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b22166f51707f0f611ab05369d6065bfa17f644","tid":2274414,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc39e5d67e5ceb9e3a5328ff9436282c56fe6bc1","tid":2274414,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n又黎<br />\n<br />\n中大已經係咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"中大而家唔係曬證登記入得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:11:40.000Z","msg":"中大唔比人搞一週年<br />\n理大又係咁<br />\n<br />\n我想指咁G<br />\n獨立自主就係笑話"},{"pid":"06cf868a9aeb10f6260cbacd3ae1b1e679f0098f","tid":2274414,"uid":310074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"封校就唔發酵喇咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ec84d5fe3b326e30cfe45da7179c3999873